{"tid":1714883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲入黎鼓勵返元朗班手足！！","createTime":"2019-11-13T03:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:28:48.000Z","uid":118949,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"999be03de1c9f243a82022ad9a5f61b31c81d445","tid":1714883,"uid":118949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/104804407605712/posts/127927628626723?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F104804407605712%2Fposts%2F127927628626723%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE9%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=57a26e26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/104804407605712/posts/127927628626723?vh=e&amp;d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n事源我喺FB見到原來今日元朗手足做緊野嘅時候，有唔少藍絲鬧走佢地。<br />\n<br />\n我屌你呀！唔係因為佢地，你地死撚左好耐喇！而家鬧撚走佢地？？周圍都放火？！又唔見你話警曱周圍打人同開搶？！盲毛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足對唔住，我唔喺現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望冇下次，就算有，我都一撚定幫你地頂住，因為手足不是condom，不分化不割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n最係呢度有藍絲五毛mon po狗覺得佢地鬧得啱嘅話，我想同你講，你真係有呢份咁勇敢反抗嘅心就唔該拎出黎對付殺人政權！唔撚係攞黎對付被政府逼出黎嘅示威者！欺善怕惡冇撚用架！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55629241d05b132b5737a106ef8002f168b51734","tid":1714883,"uid":30081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"除左中大之外，希望各院舍都申請禁制令唔好令黑警入內<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1714563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1714563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8ae3f6590d6fd05407d2b8aef953eed1ae90333e","tid":1714883,"uid":193138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-